-- S.African state pension fund says Abil "almost like a bottomless pit" 
-- By Tiisetso Motsoeneng
-- Wed Aug 06, 2014 05:49AM EDT
-- None



JOHANNESBURG, Aug 6 (Reuters) - South Africa's state pension fund said on Wednesday that struggling African Bank Investments <ABLJ.J> was "almost like a bottomless pit" after the unsecured lender warned of a $600 million full-year loss and said it would launch its second big capital raising in about a year.

